# IKE Project JVM Configuration
# Do NOT set -Denv.PATH or PATH-related options here or in MAVEN_OPTS.
# PATH entries containing spaces (e.g. JetBrains Toolbox) cause Java
# to fail with "Could not find or load main class" errors.

# Suppress JFFI sun.misc.Unsafe deprecation warnings from JRuby/AsciidoctorJ
--sun-misc-unsafe-memory-access=allow
